snippet.title: Cosplay Club  - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Now on Kickstarter, until November 3rd, 2022. 
http://playcosplayclub.com

In this tactical turn-based RPG you'll embark on the journey of becoming a Magical Girl cosplayer! But don't let this journey fool you, because this is not just roleplaying: your costumes will give you real life powers, and the world's fate will be in your hands!

Coming soon in 2023 to PC and major Consoles. Join our discord to know more: http://www.discord.gg/beholdstudios
